i. Our\npolarimetric evidence is supported by the results of simulation of dust cloud\nformation in the L5 point of the Earth-Moon system presented in the first part\nof this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 2019 16:53:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-17"}
