 from a\nquantum-field-theoretic perspective and comment on implications of our findings\nfor the interpretation of experiments on quantum critical heavy-fermion\ncompounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 2019 18:00:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Feb 2020 19:53:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 6 Mar 2020 21:06:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-10"}
