ately, we propose a novel pathway to uncover the depth\ndependence of local surface material properties for more complete,\nnon-destructive, microstructural characterization, through nanoindentation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 2019 19:49:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Feb 2020 13:09:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-04"}
