inties, the nuclear\nmodification factor is particle species independent for high $p_{\\rm{T}}$ and\ncompatible with measurements at $\\sqrt{s_{\\rm{NN}}}$ = 2.76 TeV. The results\nare compared to state-of-the-art model calculations, which are found to\ndescribe the observed trends satisfactorily.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Oct 2019 02:04:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2020 23:10:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-17"}
