 phase stiffness. On the other hand,\nthe second onset $T_2^{\\text{ons}}$ is identified at substantially higher than\n$T_{\\text{c}}$, whose origin is discussed in terms of preformed Cooper pairs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Oct 2019 03:38:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 02:44:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 16 Aug 2020 07:40:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-18"}
