anowire axis allowed to directly image the\nnanoscale localization of the emission, supporting the above picture. Our\nfindings contribute to a deeper understanding of the luminescence-structure\nrelationship in QWT nanowires and will foster their applications as efficient\nnanolaser sources for future monolithic integration onto silicon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Oct 2019 08:23:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-18"}
